&lt;h1 id="feb-3-2020-week-1">Feb 3, 2020 (Week 1)&lt;/h1>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Duration: 1 hour&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Participants: 5 - 6 people&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="before-this-session">before this session:&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>writing letters&lt;/li>
&lt;li>mindmap&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Ch12: many Checklist to fill in&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="agenda">Agenda&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Part 1 (40min): Present yourself with a title and 5 min speech, half an hour or more, to find and convince another guy to be your buddy&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Part 2 (20min): Discuss&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Part 3: We choose our buddy, make a team (2 or 3 members in a team)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h1 id="feb-10-2020-week-2">Feb 10, 2020 (Week 2)&lt;/h1>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Part 1 (40min): Present our team (the team name, describe your first starting action), 10 min, half an hour or more&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Part 2 (20min): Discuss&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Part 3: Vote for the winner team&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="teams">Teams&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Shukka &amp;amp; Mia (Giselle)&lt;/li>
